{"tid":309360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"16歲少年與71歲老婦譜婆孫戀 揚言若家人阻撓婚事就雙雙殉情","createTime":"2017-07-05T03:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T01:31:09.000Z","uid":22349,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eaeec654ac5fbff12d1f9568c3454bf4fac3f04b","tid":309360,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:13:26.000Z","msg":"印尼一名16歲少年與一名71歲女子結婚，揚言如果家人阻撓婚事，他們就雙雙殉情。<br />\n<br />\n從婚禮片段所見，薩拉馬特（Selamat Riayadi）與羅哈雅（Rohaya）雖然相差55歲，但都表示深愛對方，願意雙宿雙棲。<br />\n<br />\n而兩人都不富有，薩拉馬特家人給女家的禮金，僅20萬印尼盾（119港元）。<br />\n<br />\n當地社區領袖庫斯沃約（Kuswoyo）證實，薩拉馬特與羅哈雅的確已成夫婦，又表示他們曾經揚言，如果婚事被阻，不惜雙雙殉情。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日鏡報》"},{"pid":"07f63abc45ea5f3128abcce16e26ea4a2456c0df","tid":309360,"uid":22349,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:14:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170705/large/1499199414_007a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170705%2Flarge%2F1499199414_007a.jpg&h=287684e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54e7c9569776f0e2cca3a1d44c63e31a4ea05e27","tid":309360,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:14:16.000Z","msg":"鏡報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b64a9d8efa88bfcb0bd9cb3fe4eb5b2e2dc7c58","tid":309360,"uid":108311,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:17:33.000Z","msg":"古道熱腸"},{"pid":"4fde71b2bb50a3226c4276166f798da0d5270bff","tid":309360,"uid":46420,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:20:04.000Z","msg":"正宗小朋友幹大姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f65c10258236b3212023e4fba20042c1425f555","tid":309360,"uid":27919,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:21:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正宗小朋友幹大姐姐<